    <!-- DEPLOYMENT TEXT -->
    <string name="about_text">Mapping the Mangroves is a project focused on tracking/mapping the biodiversity of coastal
        ecosystems and raising public awareness about this vital habitat. The project aims to connect and mobilize a
        global network of proactive, environmentally-engaged citizens who collect and disseminate information about the
        world\'s mangroves. The project\'s ultimate goal will be to provide students, educators and scientists around the
